*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+ REQUIREMENTS +*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*
	Server / ISP:
		- Linux oder MacosX, (NO Windows!)
		- Apache HTTP Server (or similar, must support .htaccess) => http://httpd.apache.org/download.cgi
		- PHP >= 5.2 => http://www.php.net/downloads.php , no early php5/php4 (full of bugs)! 
           + Imap Library + Mysql Lib + GD-Lib
           
           (Tellmatic is developed and tested under PHP5.2 stable releases + suhosin + fcgi)
		- Mysql >= v4.1 (Mysql 4.1.x/5.x, NO Mysql3!)
           (Tellmatic is developed and tested under Mysql5 stable releases)
		- Access to SMTP, POP3 and/or IMAP Server
		- Optional: Cronjobs, PHP CLI or wget (Cronjobs execute at least every 10 Min. to be effective)
    
    Client:   
       standard Browser with Javascript support (Seamonkey, Mozilla or Firefox, IE (limited, no 24Bit PNG support))
       IE Support is limited1 Please use a standard browser.

*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+ BASIC-FEATURES V1.0.x +*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*+*
	Easy installation, installed in 2 minutes
	Comfortable and intuitive web frontend
	Multiuser
	Online help
	Multilingual
	Filemanager
	Linkmanager
	Quality checks
	Search for double entries
	Different styles for frontend
	Wysiwyg Online-Editor (TinyMCE) & spellchecker	
	Blacklist (blacklist by email, domain or regular expression)
	Multiple mailservers for SMTP and POP3/IMAP (maildelivery and bouncemanagement)
	Graphical statistics
	Geographical maps (subscriptions, readers, etc.), using GeoIP API and database
	Scheduled mail delivery, (with cronjobs), write now, send in two weeks
	Multiple address-/recipientgroups per address (private and public groups, define default groups/subcribers can choose from public groups etc)
	Unlimited! Unlimited amount of emails, newsletter etc, no hardcoded Limits! (Just depends on your server settings)
	Newslettergroups
	Newsletter Templates
	Bouncemanagement
	Duplicate Checking!
	Errormanagement, delivery-errors, address-errors etc
	Statistics and reports
	"Clean Up Database"-Feature (delete, move, set status of failed addresses etc.)
	Email-Reports 
	Click-/Linktracker
	Viewtracker (blank blindimage, or any other png/jpg)
	Linkmanager and Link-Tracking, Links can be personalized 
	personalized Tracking option
	Email validation (3 levels for internal and subscriptions, import etc)
	CSV address import
	CSV address export
	Personalized newsletter (add a private salutation etc, track clicks, views etc.)
	Massmailing (send anonymized newsletter)
	View personalized Newsletter online
	Delivery via SMTP
	Double opt-in/out
	Subscription-form-generator
	Unlimited attachments
	
	and much more...	

